<i>adverb</i>: 안전히 [안전히], 성히 [성히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>안전히 [안전히]</dt><br>
<dd>safely</dd><br>
<dd>위험이 생기거나 사고가 나지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that one does not fall into danger or become the victim of an accident.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>성히 [성히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. intact</dd><br>
<dd>물건이 처음 모습처럼 온전히.</dd><br>
<dd>Wholly, the same as its original form.</dd><br>
<dd>2. healthily; safely</dd><br>
<dd>몸에 병이나 탈이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without disease or trouble.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>